Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:55.25,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.34,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,あっあ…　困る？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.34,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,啊…  不方便嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.09,0:10:58.97,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:58.97,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.26,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,電車代　高いから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.26,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,車票  很貴的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.39,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,バイトする
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.39,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我會打工的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.64,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,私もする
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.64,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我也去打工
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.68,0:11:05.51,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,陸部は？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:05.51,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,那田徑部呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.42,0:11:08.81,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,続けたいけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:08.81,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我也想繼續…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.48,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,俺が行くから大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.48,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,那就我去找你吧  沒事的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.02,0:11:14.15,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,週３くらいバイトすれば　電車賃なんとかなるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:14.15,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,每週打工三次  車票還是賺得到的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.03,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,片道　２時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.03,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,單程要兩小時？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.36,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,始発で行く
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.36,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,那就坐早班車去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.03,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.03,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.66,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,長くいられる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.66,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,這樣就能待久一點
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.87,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,今までと変わんないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.87,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,還是和以前一樣的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.37,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ラインもあるし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.37,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,而且還有LINE
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.04,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,けど…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.04,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.38,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,小太郎君ばっかりつらいのって…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.38,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,不能總讓小太郎一個人辛苦…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.17,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,平気平気
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.17,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.05,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,私も貯金あるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.05,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我也有存款的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.97,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,無理しなくていいって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.97,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你不用勉強的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.89,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,そうじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.89,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.02,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,茜ちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.02,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小茜…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.11,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,聞きたいことあって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.11,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我有事想問你
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.40,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.40,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.36,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,告られたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.36,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你被告白了嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.03,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,千夏に聞いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.03,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,千夏告訴我了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.79,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,そうだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.79,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,是被告白了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.75,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,なんで…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.75,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.29,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,言ってくれなかったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.29,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,不告訴我呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.67,0:12:22.80,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,それは…　俺　断ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:22.80,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,因為…  我拒絕掉了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.31,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,言わない？　普通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.31,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,這種事  都不說嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.06,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,心配になるもん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.06,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我好擔心
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,え？　どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,欸？  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.94,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,分かんないけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.94,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.10,0:13:00.88,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,なんで？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:00.88,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.14,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,私…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.14,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.31,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ずっと…　不安で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.31,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,一直…  很不安
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.18,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,不安で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.18,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,很不安
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.40,0:13:20.02,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,小太郎君に　迷惑ばっかり…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:20.02,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,總是給你  添麻煩…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.61,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,それが　一番つらい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.61,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,這個是最痛苦的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.25,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,どうしたらいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.25,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我到底該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.36,0:15:33.03,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,母さん　これ捨てていいんだっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:33.03,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,孩子她媽  這個能扔掉嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.37,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,これってどれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.37,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,這個是哪個啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.41,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,業者さん邪魔しちゃダメよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.41,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,別給搬家公司的人添麻煩
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.08,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,お母さん　業者さん呼んでるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.08,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽  搬家公司的人叫你
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.96,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,パパに言って
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.96,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,叫你爸爸去
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.93,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,茜　忘れ物ない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.93,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小茜  沒忘東西吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.23,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.23,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.60,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\an7}これじゃ最後で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.60,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}這是最後一件了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.60,0:16:28.17,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\an9}ちょうどいい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:28.17,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an9}剛剛好
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.21,0:16:30.51,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ヤバい　鼻づっついてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:30.51,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不好 又想哭了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.95,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ホントありがとうね　２人とも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.95,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,真的很感謝你們兩個
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.30,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,寂しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.30,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,這下要寂寞了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.51,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,またもう…　やめてよね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.51,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,又來了…  別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.43,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ちょっと　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.43,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,等等  喂
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.02,0:16:47.86,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,またね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:47.86,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.61,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.61,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.48,0:16:50.90,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:50.90,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.28,0:16:52.99,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:52.99,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.49,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,茜はあとから電車で来るかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.49,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小茜要不要晚點再坐電車過來？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.37,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,え　いいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.37,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,欸  可以嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.33,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,せっかく友達来てるんだし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.33,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,難得朋友來送你了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.29,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ゆっくり話したいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.29,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你也想再聊一會對吧
