Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.46,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,啊  那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.84,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.84,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.42,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,待ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.42,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,等等啊
