Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:16.68,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你看這個
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.76,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,見つけちゃったんだ　私
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.76,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我偶然發現的
