Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.78,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,說起來  我看過你的網路小說了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.28,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,えっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.28,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.95,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,更新してるじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.95,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,更新了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.95,0:19:01.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:01.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.82,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,結構コメント付いてるね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.82,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,評論挺多嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.08,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ほら　ここ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.08,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你看  這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.38,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,よかったじゃん　好評だし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.38,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,挺不錯嘛  好評如潮
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.06,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　気をつけてね茜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.06,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,路上小心哦  小茜
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.23,0:19:34.69,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:34.69,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
