Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.90,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,要來找我們玩哦
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.19,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.19,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.40,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,それじゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.40,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,再見了
